   <head>Lirica latina - Lirica III</head>
  </front>
  <body>
   <lg xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" type="poem">
    <lg n="1">
     <l n="1">Stirps Areosta fuit, Ferraria patria, Fulcus</l>
     <l n="2">nomen, Roma altrix, Appula humus tegit hic.</l>
     <l n="3">Tormento ictus obi, dum Ripae a moenibus arcens</l>
     <l n="4">Fernandum Ursino pro duce praesideo.</l>
     <l n="5">Octavam vixi trieterida. Caetera, quaeso,</l>
     <l n="6">disce aliunde; nefas me mea facta loqui.</l>
    </lg>
   </lg>
  </body>
